            <p class="text-gray-700">Squarespace's templates communicate stability and professionalism. Clean layouts, strong typography, organized sections. Perfect for insurance agents wanting established credibility. Shoppers see polished site = legitimate agent = trust = quote request.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">2. Built-in Quote Forms</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Integrated forms connect to your email immediately. Customize fields: name, email, phone, coverage type, ZIP code, "best time to call." Auto-responder confirms receipt. One agent added "We Respond Within 2 Hours"ÊâøËØ∫: 89% higher conversion to policy sold.</p>
